  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户旅程图，展示用户从登录到完成一次训练记录的全流程。核心场景是康复训练App，用户要先认证，然后规划训练，最后记录实际完成情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Authentication",
        "Dashboard",
        "Planner",
        "Logger",
        "Progress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，康复训练场景。旅程图需要分几个阶段？我初步想拆成：登录认证、首页看板、训练规划、实际记录、还有进度回顾。这样五个section够吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Authentication",
        "section Dashboard",
        "section Planner",
        "section Logger",
        "section Progress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "五个section可以。认证部分要体现2FA，因为涉及健康数据，安全要求高。Dashboard那里用户应该能看到\"下一次计划训练\"，然后有个入口去规划新的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Enter credentials & 2FA",
        "View next planned session",
        "Click \"Plan new session\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先加上认证和Dashboard部分。认证里放：打开登录页、输入凭证和2FA、后端验证跳转。Dashboard放查看下次计划训练，以及点击\"规划新训练\"的按钮。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Open login page",
        "Enter credentials & 2FA",
        "Backend validates, redirects",
        "View next planned session",
        "Click \"Plan new session\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是Planner部分。用户点击后进入规划界面，可以添加具体训练动作，还要设置重复规则，比如每周几次。最后保存这个计划。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Planner",
        "Add exercises & recurrence",
        "Save planned session"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Planner加好了。然后Logger部分我理解是：用户打开之前规划好的训练，记录实际做的组数、重量这些，最后标记完成。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Open planned session",
        "Record actuals",
        "Mark as complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "对，但记录实际数据那里要特别强调一下——我们用的是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault存储，合规要求必须标出来。可以写成\"记录实际数据（HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault）\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Record actuals (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，加上了HIPAA Vault的标注。最后Progress部分我放：打开进度看板，查看图表和连续打卡记录。这样整个旅程就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Progress",
        "Open Progress Dashboard",
        "View charts and streaks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美。整个标题就叫\"User Journey: Plan & Log a Session\"吧，准确概括这个核心闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title User Journey: Plan & Log a Session"
